description: Add vegetables into this muffin mixture.  The kids will love them without knowing they are filled with healthy vegetables.
keywords: Savoury muffin,Zucchini,Seafood free,Soy free,Tree nut free,Pumpkin,Sesame free,Spinach,Peanut free
name: Vegetable Savoury Muffins Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Turn oven on at 180 degrees. Sift self-raising flour into a bowl.
Add all other ingredients, except for the pumpkin, and mix well.
Add the pumpkin and gently mix. You don't want to mash the pumpkin, so be careful when mixing it in with the other ingredients.
Spray muffin tin with Olive Oil. Spoon into 12 cup muffin tray. Cook at 180 for 20 mins.
